Review Text: I went to check out if there were any discounts for the Eid season.  And I was duly rewarded.  One of the sales persons (Mr Badar) was so very courteous and helpful that I actually offered him a job.  But he is in his first year of university ( electrical and computer engineering) and was just doing this part time. Got two pairs of jeans and three shirts.  The next day I went again and bought stuff for my son. Good quality at good prices.
